title: Best signs from College GameDay in Ann Arbor

(WXYZ) - ESPN's College GameDay was in Ann Arbor on Saturday morning ahead of the Michigan State versus Michigan game at The Big House. 
With GameDay in town, that also means the students' signs were out in full force, throwing shots at everyone from Mark D'Antonio, Connor Cook, and even some brave Michigan State fans picking on Jim Harbaugh. 
Check out some of the best signs below from the College GameDay Twitter account . Jon Snow lives. (Please?) pic.twitter.com/gBfULLeIGL â€” College GameDay (@CollegeGameDay) October 17, 2015 Only way to spend a Saturday. pic.twitter.com/5E2vT9PgSa
